# Copy to .streamlit/secrets.toml for local runs, or paste into the
# Streamlit Community Cloud app's "Secrets" settings panel.
#
# The dashboard currently needs no secrets: the champion model is loaded
# from the committed models/champion.joblib file, not a database or an
# external API. This file exists as a placeholder for when that changes
# (e.g. a hosted feature store or a remote scoring API key).
